Merges the results of the weekly and daily scrapes.

Creates a map of run IDs → dataset IDs, marking each as:
  status: false (not processed yet)

If today matches the weekly day (Monday), it includes both;
otherwise, only daily data.

Returns:
  {
    ids: { runId: { status, datasetId } },
    succeeded: 0
  }

